Diamond-Star Motors Corp, thejoint-venture company owned by Chrysler Corp &lt;C> and MitsubishiMotors, said it has additional product suppliers for theall-new vehicle to be produced at the company's plant now underconstruction.    It said Globe Industries Inc, Chicago Heights, Ill., waspicked to supply roof silencer pads and dash panel pads, andFabricon Products of River Rouge, Mich., for hood insulators. Reuter&#3;